Sunny- breezy- cool.  Hawk near shore.
Very cloudy- windy.  65 degrees.  Saw a loon- 3 ducks- seagull and a red necked grebe.
Very cloudy- the temperautre is 66 degrees.  Color past peak around lake.  Saw 14 mallards- 66 seagulls- 1 crow and 1 bald eagle flying over Seed Lake.
38 degrees.  Overcast.  Birch and aspen leaves gold.  Saw 3 crows.
Partly cloudy breezy.  Tree swallow chickadee  and crow.
Sunny and slightly cloudy.  Calm.  Saw 5 ducks in a tree swallow.
Partly cloudy saw 2 tree swallows- eagle- 2 kites or merlins and a loon.
Overcast and calm.  2 loons. bottom is at 26 feet.
Partly cloudy.  Bottom is at 25 feet deep.  Bald eagle.
Windy and sunny.  Loon 2 ring-billed gulls
Partly sunny and cloudy.  7 seagulls and 1 eagle.
Sunny and calm few clouds.  12 mallards and 3 seagulls.
Sunny and calm.  1 seagull 1 loon and mallards.  6 boats.  Water level: very low.
Sunny and windy.  Slightly cloudy.  7 seagulls.  Water level: very low.
Sunny to partly cloudy and calm.  1 loon and 7 seagulls.  Water level: very low.
Partly cloudy and windy.  1 loon and 3 gulls.  Water level: very low.
Sunny to partly cloudy.  1 loon 8 ducks and 3 gulls.  Water level: very low.
Sunny and breezy.  Bald eagle and loon and seagull.  Lake full of algae. looks very bad esp. near shore.  Worst we have seen for algae growth.
No clouds. sunny. breezy. aspen leaves coming out. 75 F. 1 loon- 1 duck- 3 tree swallows- 2 boats. 24.25' deep.
A few clouds. calm. sunny. leaves coming out. temperature low 60s. 1 tree swallow- 1 loon- 2 boats. 26'. deep aspen fuzz.
Sunny. windy. clear. 75 F. bald eagle- 1 loon- 3 ducks- male + female swallows (on shore) - 5 boats. 22' deep.
Windy. Very cloudy. 23.5' deep. sunny. 3 bald eagles- 2 tree swallows- 1 duck- 2 boats. 76 F.
Partly cloudy. calm. 75 F. 2 boats- 1 bald eagle with fish- 4 red-winged blackbirds- 1 tree swallow- crayfish + 2 large fish near shore. 22.25' deep.
67 F. Breezy. Sunny. A few clouds. Depths at 25.5'. 1 boat- 1 adult loon- 1 common crow.
Sunny. clear. slight breeze. 5 boats. 75 F.  25.5' deep.  1 loon. 1 bald eagle.
Sunny. a few clouds. wind-calm. 85 F. 4 boats- 1 jet ski. 25.5' deep.  1 loon- 1 bald eagle.
6 boats. 71 F. Sunny. A few clouds. Calm. 26' deep. A few very small fish near shore.
Sunny. some clouds. calm. 2 seagulls- 1 eagle or hawk. 25' deep.
Sunny- cloudy- breezy. 70 F. 1 boat- 1 loon- 1 seagull- 1 bluejay- 1 belted kingfisher. 26' deep.
54 F. sunny- a few clouds- calm- 26' deep- 1 immature loon- 1 seagull.
2 boats- 1 immature loon- 1 seagull- sunny- cloudy- 25' deep- windy- 65 F. Some fall color.
1 common loon- sunny- clear- breezy- no leaves on hardwoods- tamaracks golden- 1 boat- about 24' deep.
Sunny- 66 degrees with a few clouds. slight breeze. blue heron- blackbird- heard ducks and crows.
Cloudy- 60 degrees- windy. bald eagle caught fish from lake.
Partly cloudy- 73 degrees. blue heron near shore- adult eagle- 1 calling loon- rw blackbird.
74 degrees- partly cloudy- breezy.  2 osprey- bald eagle- loon- 2 turtles in water.
72 degrees- partly cloudy- calm.  1 robin- 1 loon- 1 duck
74 degrees- sunny- clear with light breeeze.  1 loon- 4 boats.
Sunny- few clouds- breezy. 7 boats- 3 gulls- 2 loons.
61 degrees- breezy- sunny. 1 immature loon- 4 mallards- 1 eagle- 2 ducks.
72 degrees- sunny- a few clouds- light breeze.  Adult and immature loon- 1 heron- 2 boats.
60 degrees- sunny and breezy. 2 gulls- 4 boats.
72 degrees- sunny. 2 ducks- 1 gull- heard loon and eagle.
Sunny- partly cloudy- breezy- 70 degrees.  1 immature loon- 1 blue jay- 1 turkey vulture- 9 gulls- 3 boats.
3 tree swallows- male and female mallard.  Cloudy- sunny- calm.  Sample at 23.5 deep.  2 boats.

81 F- sunny- cloudy- light breeze- 5 boats.  Sample at 25' deep.  1 common loon.
6 boats- 69 F- sunny- partly cloudy- breezy- 7 seagulls- 2 loons- 1 American crow.  Sample at 23' deep.
80 F- 3 boats- 1 loon- 1 seagull.  Sunny- partly cloudy- light wind.  Sample at 23' deep.
A lot of fall color- almost clear skies- sunny- 57 F.  2 boats.  Breezy- 1 seagull.  Sample at 22' deep.
51-53 degrees- sunny- partly cloudy- 1 loon- breezy- 1 boat- at 23' deep. ICE OFF: 4/18/02.
82 degrees- 5 boats- sunny and partly cloudy- 1 tree swallow- at 24.25' deep.
